Package: rplo5
Type: Package
Title: Fast 5-Card PLO Equity and Percentile Calculations
Version: 0.2.0
Author: You
Maintainer: You <f0uts123456@gmail.com>
Description: Monte Carlo and exact equity calculations for 5-card Pot Limit
    Omaha (2-6 players), with hand-strength percentile rankings both preflop
    (static table) and conditional on a flop, turn or river. Wraps a fast
    multithreaded C engine.
